[ plateform ]
raspberry pi, for inet connectivity and LINUX support


[ communication ]
http endpoint
reverse communication using http or email


[ persistent storage ]
able to reapply the last configuration if power goes down


[ notification system ]
email sms alerts
transport layers: email, sms


[ implementation ]
C for low level hardware access
javascript for nodejs and email support


[ email notifications ]

[[ implementation ]]
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4113701/sending-emails-in-node-js
https://github.com/andris9/Nodemailer

[[ event ]]
system reboot
ip changed


[ nodejs ]

[[ cross compile ]]
http://n8.io/cross-compiling-nodejs-v0.8/
refer to do_configure_node.sh
note that it might be required to edit out/Makefile and set LINK.target

[[ nodemailer ]]
install nodemailer module locally using npm: npm install nodemailer
running node js: NODE_PATH=../node_modules node mailer.js

[[ rpib gpios ]]
https://npmjs.org/package/pi-gpio
npm install pi-gpio